data.description: Location! Location! Location!  This wonderful 3 bedroom 2 bath home in the NE neighborhood of Pine Ridge Estates, nestled on .41 acres on a quiet cul-de-sac.  This home features a formal living room, family room/playroom, dining room, spacious kitchen, large walk in pantry and nice big bedrooms.  Large back yard with mature trees and landscaping.  NO HOA! Close to shopping, walking trails, kayaking, fishing and so much more.  Schedule a tour today.
